{"data":{"wpProject":{"projectMeta":{"projectId":"518","project":"Piramal Mahalaxmi"}},"wpLogo":{"logoMeta":{"logo":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/startlogo-1.png"}}},"wpOffer":{"offerMeta":{"offer1":"ZERO PRE-EMI*","offer2":"BOOK NOW & SAVE UP TO RS 39 LACS","offer3":"20:80 EASY PAYMENT PLAN","offer4":"ZERO STAMP DUTY","offer5":"Lavish 2, 3 & 4 BHK","offer6":null}},"allWpBanner":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerMeta":{"deviceType":"MOBILE","imageUpload":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mobile-banner_2.jpg"}}}},{"node":{"bannerMeta":{"deviceType":"DESKTOP","imageUpload":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/banner1.jpeg"}}}},{"node":{"bannerMeta":{"deviceType":"DESKTOP","imageUpload":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Web-banner.jpg"}}}},{"node":{"bannerMeta":{"deviceType":"MOBILE","imageUpload":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mobile-banner.jpg"}}}}]},"wpOverview":{"overviewMeta":{"lessDescription":"<p>Piramal Mahalaxmi is a part of a vision to create a living space that will transport you to a lifestyle unlike any other in the city, a place where you can be at the heart of a bustling metropolis and yet cocooned from it. Piramal Mahalaxmi South Mumbai residences offer stunning views of Mahalaxmi Racecourse, the Arabian Sea, Willingdon sports club, Mumbai Harbour, and the magnetic South Mumbai Skyline. Piramal Mahalaxmi Homes are surrounded by an enviable panorama that includes the city’s most notable landmarks and major hubs, offering one an opportunity to unwind and relax with breath-taking views of nature and the city.</p>\n","moreDescription":"<p>Piramal Mahalaxmi Tower 3 embodies the spirit of Mahalaxmi and mirrors South Mumbai’s essence with its three phenomenal towers. Piramal Mahalaxmi Residence at offers endless views of South Mumbai and beyond. Piramal Mahalaxmi has been voted as the Luxury Development of the year by Realty+ at the Conclave and Excellence Awards 2020. The unparalleled amenities and choices at Piramal Mahalaxmi South Mumbai have been carefully selected to fulfill the needs of the most discerning dwellers.</p>\n<p>Piramal Mahalaxmi residents can also enjoy exclusive amenities dedicated solely to each tower apart from the common amenities. Piramal Mahalaxmi Residences are crafted with expertise, inspired by the rich palette of the city skyline. Piramal Mahalaxmi Tower 3 homes offer lifetime mesmerizing views of Racecourse &amp; Arabian Sea. The amenities at Piramal Mahalaxmi are second to none. Piramal Mahalaxmi South Mumbai&#8217;s every effort has been incorporated to create an environment that exceeds all expectations. Piramal Mahalaxmi Tower 3 is complemented by stunning views.</p>\n"}},"allWpHighlight":{"edges":[{"node":{"projectHighlightMeta":{"description":"Piramal Mahalaxmi is Spread across 4 acres & Total of 390 units of different configurations.\r\n","image":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Piramal-favicon-1.png"}}}},{"node":{"projectHighlightMeta":{"description":"Piramal Mahalaxmi offers a Premium 2, 3 & 4 Bed City View Residence.\r\n","image":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Piramal-favicon-1.png"}}}},{"node":{"projectHighlightMeta":{"description":"Piramal Mahalaxmi South Mumbai enjoys a Stunning View of the Mahalaxmi Racecourse.\r\n","image":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Piramal-favicon-1.png"}}}},{"node":{"projectHighlightMeta":{"description":"Piramal Mahalaxmi Tower 3 also enjoys a tranquil view of the Arabian sea.\r\n","image":{"sourceUrl":"http://ginfomedia.in/production/primalmahalaxmi/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Piramal-favicon-1.png"}}}},{"node":{"projec